-- Apollo Solar Says Outstanding Convertibles Change Hands for HK$500 Million
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-11-02T13:18:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/apollo-solar-says-convertible-bonds-sell-for-hk-500-million.html
China Gogreen Assets Investment Ltd .
bought  Apollo Solar Energy Technology Holdings Ltd . convertible
bonds with a face value of HK$329 million from GS-Solar (Cayman)
Co. for HK$500 million, according to Apollo’s filing to Hong
Kong’s stock exchange today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  